GCA3AUD.original: ~z~Sorry, Mr. European but I want to keep those mysterious bits of you, mysterious.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~抱歉，欧洲先生，但我还是想让你神秘的地方保持神秘。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~That was really biting social commentary, wasn't it?
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~对社会的批判十分尖锐，不是吗？

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~Can you take me home?
~z~Let me in and I promise to be gentle.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~让我进去吧，我保证会温柔的。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, later.
~z~How about we find something else to do now?
~z~It used to be impossible to get a table there and you can see why.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~以前这里一席难求，原因你也能看出来。

GCA3AUD.original: GCA_ACT_LEAVE_SHOW_COMEDY
GCA_ACT_POOL_LEAVE_ABANDON
~z~Great, you won at darts. It must be fun for you.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~好，飞镖你比我强。你高兴了吧。

GCA3AUD.original: GCA_ACT_PAL_END_YES
~z~This hasn't exactly been the date of my dreams, Niko. But what did I expect?
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~这跟我想象中的约会不大一样，Niko。不过我还能指望什么呢？

GCA3AUD.original: GCA_ACT_PAL_END_KISS_AGREE
GCA_ACT_PAL_END_KISS
~z~You want me to come in?
~z~God, the stories I could tell you about this place, let's walk.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~天哪，我有很多关于这里的故事可以讲，边走边聊吧。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~See ya.
GCA_ACT_POOL_LEAVE_WON
~z~Those girls have had some serious work done. I want the name of the honey colored one's doctor.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~那些女人整形整得很厉害。我想知道那个金发女人的整形医生的名字。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~I'd love to be taken home now.
~z~Yeah, yeah, I get it.
~z~I'd like that Niko.
~z~That was an immaculate dining experience.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~刚才的用餐体验真的是完美极了。

GCA3AUD.original: GCA_ACT_ARRIVE_WALK_LAST
~z~How about you invite me in?
~z~Woo hoo, Niko beats Alex at pool - a game she incidentally hates. Stop the press.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~呜呼，Niko在台球上打败了Alex，她最讨厌台球了。别吹了。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~Bye then.
~z~I guess that's my life story, thanks for listening.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~那大概就是我的人生经历，感谢收听。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~This has been an interesting experience
GCA_ACT_DATEFINISHED_OK
~z~I think we both want me to come inside.
GCA_ACT_DARTS_LEAVE_ABANDON
GCA_ACT_DARTS_LEAVE_DRAW
GCA_ACT_BORED_GETTING
~z~What's the deal with this? Where are we going?
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~这是什么意思？我们要去哪儿？

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~That place is so cool. I'm buzzed. It's amazing.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~那地方太酷了。我有点小醉，体验很棒。

GCA3AUD.original: GCA_ACT_LEAVE_CLUB_FAVOURITE
~z~Well the crowd in there was a bit B and T, wasn't it? At least I got buzzed enough to cope.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~那里面的人大多是通勤族，不是吗？至少我已经够醉了。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, let me take your number and we can go on another date sometime.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~确实，给我你的电话吧，我们以后还能再出来约会。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~Thank God it's over and we didn't even have to put all the balls in the holes.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~谢天谢地，终于结束了，再也没必要把球都打到洞里了。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~Later on then, Alex.
~z~Just because I write about sex on my blog, doesn't mean I'm going to put out.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~我在博客上面大谈特谈性的话题，不代表我要进行实践。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~Big deal, I won a game of pool. Could not care less.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~很不错，我赢了一局台球。这可不能无视。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~Do you want to do something else now?
GCA_ACT_DATEFINISHED_AGAIN
~z~I knew you'd find that story interesting. I'm really good at telling what people will like.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~我就知道你会对这个故事感兴趣。我真的很擅长讲述别人喜欢的东西。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~Bland, unmemorable, bad service. I'd give that place three out of ten.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~乏味、无趣、服务差。十分制我只能打三分。

GCA3AUD.original: GCA_ACT_ARRIVE_WALK_BEFORE
~z~Wait for me to call you, okay?
GCA_ACT_LEAVE_WALK
~z~Ending that game early was the best decision I've seen you make.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~提前结束是你至今做出的最好的决定。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~This has got to be a new low point, Niko. Being beaten by a girl who hates darts.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~实在是太糟糕了，Niko。你输给了一个讨厌飞镖的女孩。

GCA3AUD.original: GCA_ACT_ARRIVE_WALK_MHAT_LAST
~z~I'm bored and the date hasn't even started yet.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~约会还没开始我就要无聊死了。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~You won't regret this.
~z~Well I bet it feels really good to beat someone whose heart's not in the game.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~行吧，打败一个对台球没兴趣的人感觉很棒吧。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~You know, even winning at pool isn't fun.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~知道吗，台球就算赢了也没什么意思。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~Where to next my mysterious European companion?
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~接下来去哪儿，我的神秘欧洲伴侣？

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~Can we at least have some fun out here?
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~出来玩怎么说也得整点有意思的吧？

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~Okay, you won, big deal, let's go.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~好吧，你赢了，就这样，我们走吧。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~How about I come into your place?
~z~Sorry, Niko. But tonight is just not the night.
~z~Be a sweetie and drop me back at my place.
GCA_ACT_LEAVE_STRIP_OKAY
~z~I'll call you, I promise.
~z~I feel like I totally understand a new culture now.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~感觉我完全理解了这种新文化。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~Screw this.
~z~From now on I am only dating Americans.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~从现在起，我只跟美国人约会。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~You can take me back to my place now.
~z~This date better not be all foreplay and no pay off. Can we get where we're going already?
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~这次约会最好别全是前戏没有结局。我们到地方了吗？

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~No dice cowboy, I'm keeping myself company tonight.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~没门儿，牛仔，今晚我已经有伴了。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~Okay, yeah.
GCA_ACT_DATEFINISHED_GOOD
~z~I'm always going to love that place, the people are so beautiful. I belong there.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~我向来喜欢那个地方，那里的人都很美。我属于那里。

GCA3AUD.original: GCA_ACT_DARTS_LEAVE_LOST
~z~I just don't feel like inviting you in yet.
GCA_ACT_BORED_HOME
GCA_ACT_PAL_END_KISS_RESPONSE
~z~Niko, I've been diagnosed with ADHD, I don't like having to wait this long to get where we're going.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~Niko，我被诊断有多动症，不喜欢在中途等这么久。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~That really enlightened me as to what the European mind is like, you know?
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~它启发了我什么是欧式思维，你知道吗？

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~I could do with an escort back to my place.
GCA_ACT_PAL_END_REJECT
GCA_ACT_POOL_LEAVE_DRAW
~z~Well don't just stand there, stupid.
~z~The fun's over.
~z~You really like this spot don't you? Did a friend of yours die here?
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~你真的很喜欢这里，不是吗？是你的哪个朋友死在这里了吗？

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~The best thing about darts is getting to quit half way through.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~玩飞镖时最好的一件事就是中途结束。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~So after I checked myself out of rehab I decided that I didn't have a problem. The end.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~离开戒毒所后，我就确信我没毛病了。就这。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~I was finding that really interesting, Niko. Thanks for making me leave.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~我正在兴头上呢，Niko。真是谢谢你带我走人啊。

GCA3AUD.original: GCA_ACT_END_GOOD
GCA_ACT_LEAVE_SHOW_EARLY
~z~Can we please find something to do already?
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~能不能麻烦你赶紧安排点活动？

GCA3AUD.original: GCA_ACT_PAL_END_GOOD_N
GCA_ACT_LEAVE_PUB_GENERIC
~z~I'm done with this.
~z~There are only so many boobs a girl can look at, Niko. I think we should have left earlier.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~那里奶子太多，女孩子受不了的，Niko。我们早就该出来了。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~If you're not taking me straight home I can just call Daddy's driver.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~再不送我回去，我就打电话叫爹地的司机了。

GCA3AUD.original: GCA_ACT_LEAVE_HIGHEND
~z~See you, Alex.
~z~Would you bring me home now?
GCA_ACT_POOL_LEAVE_LOST
~z~Mmmmm, yeah.
~z~Thank God that's over. I don't think I could have finished.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~谢天谢地结束了。我都觉得自己撑不住。

GCA3AUD.original: GCA_ACT_DARTS_LEAVE_WON
~z~Let's go.
~z~It was funny because it was true, I mean don't you think?
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~说的都是大实话，所以才有趣，你不觉得吗？

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~This place carries so many memories for me, Niko. I'm so happy that I can share it with you.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~这个地方承载着我的很多回忆，Niko。很高兴我可以和你共享。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~Take me home, won't you?
~z~Really.
~z~You've shown me a good time, Niko.
~z~Goodbye, Alex.
GCA_ACT_DATEFINISHED_BAD
~z~And you've shown me that the criminals are not the only terrible people in Liberty City. Goodye.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~你也让我知道了，罪犯不是自由城里唯一一类糟糕的人。再见。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~That game was almost as anti-climactic as sex with my last boyfriend.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~刚才那局平淡得跟和我前男友做爱一样。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~I hope I wasn't boring you, I mean not that I can bore anyone, but I was talking a lot.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~希望我没有让你无聊，不是说我会让别人无聊，但我一直在说话。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~I told you I hate fast-food. I will not let it pass my lips again.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~都说了我讨厌快餐。我不会再让这种东西进我嘴里了。

GCA3AUD.original: GCA_ACT_LEAVE_STRIP_EARLY
~z~I'll go somewhere else then.
~z~We'll have fun.
~z~Okay, Niko.
GCA_ACT_PAL_END_GOOD_Y
~z~That was interesting. I've got something to put in my blog at least.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~很有趣，至少我有写博客的素材了。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~Here again, okay. There's a lot more to see in Algonquin, Niko.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~又是这儿，行吧。Algonquin能去的地方可多得很啊，Niko。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~Don't you feel pathetic? Me beating you at the sport I hate.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~你就不觉得可悲吗？我在我讨厌的项目上打败了你。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~Come over here.
~z~Enjoy yourself.
~z~That's interesting.
GCA_ACT_PAL_END_REJECT_RESPONSE
~z~That was a frat-tastic experience. It served its purpose though. I'm drunk.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~真是个普通到爆的地方。不过目的至少是达到了，我醉了。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~I haven't told that stuff to anyone before. You're a good listener.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~我之前没跟任何人说过那件事。你是一个好听众。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~I'm sorry, but I am not putting this chemical and hormone filled stuff into my body again. Will you take me somewhere else?
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~很抱歉，但我不会再让这种全是激素添加剂的东西下肚了。能不能换家店？

GCA3AUD.original: GCA_ACT_LEAVE_CLUB_GENERIC
~z~I grew up walking around here. I'm so pleased to be back.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~我小时候就在这儿晃悠。很高兴能回到这里。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~I'm always happy to come here, Niko. But there are like other places to go walking.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~能来这里我很高兴，Niko。但也有别的地方能去吧。

GCA3AUD.original: GCA_ACT_SHOW_REACT
~z~Get over here.
~z~This illustrates how un-fun darts is, there wasn't even a winner.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~你看看飞镖有多无聊，连胜负都分不出来。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~Well, I'm not going to remember that place. That's for sure.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~好吧，我不会记得那个地方的，这点可以肯定。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~I need some Ritalin.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~我需要一些利他林*。~n~(多动症治疗药)

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~Well, what can I say about our time together...
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~好吧，我对我们共处的时光无话可说...

GCA3AUD.original: GCA_ACT_LEAVE_SHOW_CABARET
~z~Umm, I don't feel like I can get physical with you right now.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~唔，我不觉得现在就能跟你有肉体关系。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~Goodnight, Alex.
~z~Umm, are you sure you want to go for a walk right now? Don't people get raped here? You better protect me.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~唔，你确定要现在散步吗？走这里很容易被强奸吧？你最好能保护我。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~Niko, this area looks very dangerous. People get killed outside of Algonquin. I trust you though.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~Niko，这地方看起来很危险。Algonquin以外的地方有很多杀人案。不过我相信你。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~As I said, that was repulsive. I am never, I mean ne-ver going there again.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~我说了，那地方很恶心。我再也、再也不会去那里了。

GCA3AUD.original: GCA_ACT_PAL_END_NO
~z~Well, let's check out this exciting place one more time. Fingers crossed we won't be killed.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~行吧，那就再去那儿瞧瞧吧。但愿我们不会被杀。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~Sorry, Niko. You're sweet but we can't do that right now.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~抱歉，Niko。你很可爱，但我们现在还不能做那个。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~There is other stuff we can do, isn't there?
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~我们应该还有别的事能做吧，不是吗？

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~Did we have to go? What? Were you getting jealous of me and the other girls or were you too turned on?
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~一定要走吗？咋了？你是嫉妒我和其它女孩一起还是太性奋了？

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~Will you take me back to my place?
~z~Shit, to think that I used to love that place. Well, I still get drunk there though.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~我靠，以前我居然还喜欢那地方。好吧，不过我还是在那儿喝醉了。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~Do you want to take me somewhere else?
~z~Do you take all your girls here, Niko? Because I'm getting to know it pretty well.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~你是不是把每个女朋友都往这儿带，Niko？因为我什么都知道。

GCA3AUD.original: GCA_ACT_END_BAD
~z~It's been a blast.
~z~You're not going to go in and be all alone, are you?
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~你也不想一个人待在家里寂寞难耐吧？

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~You know I love this place, Niko.
~z~I'm gonna call soon.
~z~Sure, goodbye.
~z~If you stay that long in a strip club, a girl is going to think that you're more interested in strippers than her.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~要是你在脱衣舞俱乐部待那么久，女孩子就会觉得比起她你更喜欢那些脱衣舞女了。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~You've shown me a good time, Niko.
~z~Oh, mmm.
GCA_ACT_DATEFINISHED_HOME
~z~We've already walked around this place once. I thought we'd seen everything there was to see. I guess not.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~我们来过这儿一次了。我还以为能看的都已经看完了。不过好像还没。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~I was just getting into that. Me and that stripper had a connection. She understood me.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~我快习惯这里了。我和那个脱衣舞女有了默契。她能懂我。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~Okay then.
GCA_ACT_PAL_END_NO_RESPONSE
~z~Enough is enough.
~z~I've enjoyed myself.
GCA_ACT_ARRIVE_WALK_MHAT_BEFORE
GCA_ACT_ARRIVE_WALK_NOT
~z~I'll write a blog about you.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~我会写一篇关于你的博客的。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~Have fun then.
GCA_ACT_PAL_END_RESPONSE
~z~I'd feel guilty if I didn't escort you all the way into your place.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~要是没有护送你进门，我会有负罪感的。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~European girls might be whores, but Americans aren't.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~欧洲女孩可能是妓女，但美国的不是。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~Can I kiss you goodbye?
~z~Niko, show some respect to the performers and stay for the length of the show.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~Niko，对表演者放尊重些，等表演结束再走。

GCA3AUD.original: ~z~Later.
GCA_ACT_PAL_END_BONK
~z~Uh huh, uh huh.
~z~Come inside then.
GCA_ACT_LEAVE_STANDARD
~z~And that's why I'm as fucked up as I am.
~z~Umm, Niko. You are taking me home, right?
GCA_ACT_ARRIVE_WALK_MHAT_NOT
GCA_ACT_LEAVE_SHOW_LATE
~z~Let me into your place, I don't bite.
~z~At least kiss me before I am sent off.
~z~The food tasted of nothing, did you notice that? Urgh.
GCA3AUD.translated: ~z~那里的菜食之无味，你有发现吗？呃。

GCA3AUD.original: GCA_ACT_LEAVE_FASTFOOD
GCA_ACT_DIFF_FASTFOOD_NO
